v1.about:
Let me help you nail your next big talk.

(My Fall Special one-on-one offer: $1499)

Here’s how we’ll work together:

1. Structure (Session 1)
→ Refine your topic and create a fresh angle
→ Filter your ideas to focus on the highest value
→ Generate a simple, memorable outline

2. Content (Sessions 2–3)
→ Craft one-liners, analogies, and stories that stick
→ Build frameworks or acronyms (if applicable)

3. Delivery (Session 4)
→ Find your authentic delivery style
→ Eliminate verbal tics and filler words
→ Manage anxiety and speak with confidence
→ Boost stage presence without being cheesy

My clients have spoken at:
→ Google
→ TEDx
→ HubSpot’s INBOUND
→ Exit Five

What they’ve said:
“Speaking to an audience of thousands feels like a walk in the park with Vince on the team.” — Ari Murray
“Vince helped me ace my talk at Google. I've never felt this comfortable doing a talk.” — Nick Broekema
“I got a standing ovation. People were walking up to me crying.” — Lashay Lewis

Want to nail your next talk?
DM me the word “Talk” or book here: https://calendly.com/vapcoaching1/30min

P.S.
Need something more custom? I also offer tailored speaking coaching and corporate workshops. Let’s chat and see what fits best.
